</div>

  </article>
  <div class="onebox-metadata">
    
    
  </div>
  <div style="clear: both"></div>
</aside>

<p>Given X11 and LD_PRELOAD, unsandboxed programs running under a regular user account can easily become root. All these things are changing with time as flatpak and Wayland support come online. However by this point then sudoless should also be safe.</p>
